The paper discusses a new method of exploring construct validity of questionnaires based on neural network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study also focuses on the use of the questionnaire in internet studies, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybersecurity (cs.CY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of the questionnaire in intercultural studies, which could be related to natural language processing (cs.CL).
